improved_metadata.title: Spray Foam Cowboy
improved_metadata.description: A humorous song about a spray foam insulation installer and their dedication to their craft. The lyrics highlight the tools, materials, and mindset of a spray foam professional.
improved_metadata.key_lyrics: I'm gonna take my hose into your home, I'm gonna spray till I can't no more
